Colorize
========

Colorize your term apps!

Requirements
------------

- Python3
- pillow
- PyYAML
- Jinja2

Quickstart
----------

- `mkdir ~/.colorize`
- `cp -r examples/* ~/.colorize/`
- grab some color palette in xresources format, in /tmp/colors for example
- `colorize new mytheme /tmp/colors`
- `colorize activate mytheme`
- Use your configuration files created in ~/.colorize/current/
- Profit!
